data.description: Nestled within the tranquil town of Kingsland Texas, awaits an extraordinary opportunity. This remarkable property has the allure of a primary residence, serene second home or a thriving investment. Boasting a successful 8-month track record as a sought-after short-term rental and Superhost, this home is ready to continue generating income while serving as your personal getaway or call it home!   Indulge in fashionable finishes and amenities throughout the home, including a Bertazzoni dual range, Fisher & Paykel dishwasher, coffee bar with pot filler, and a soaking tub with a view in the primary bedroom. Enjoy multiple living areas for relaxation and play. A small study or reading nook caters to work or leisure. Capture picturesque moments and enjoy river and hill country views from the upper deck as you savor sunsets or your morning coffee. The charming barn stands ready as a hay barn, playful kids' room or storage space.    The property's appeal is further elevated by the recent lower-level finish-out, featuring an additional HVAC unit, two bedrooms, a comfortable living space, and a convenient kitchenette. This enhancement ensures ample room for guests, family, or potential renters.   Perfectly located near Lake LBJ, The Slab, and an hour from Austin & Fredericksburg. Explore wineries, parks, historic sites and more. Make this special property yours and experience the beauty and hospitality this area has to offer, while securing a smart investment for the future.
